From af8902c7e3be8174195dead59d6a26c8fb587129 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: hellodword <46193371+hellodword@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Sat, 9 May 2026 09:48:22 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Allow OpenAI provider network timeout overrides

Permit a restricted [model_providers.openai] override table for retry and
timeout tuning while preserving the built-in OpenAI provider behavior.

Add compact_request_timeout_ms to provider config and apply it only to
/responses/compact requests when configured. Cover accepted and rejected
OpenAI overrides, default provider merging, and compact request timeout
wiring.
